        <Parent_String>gardening [300054706], forest and nature activities [300239491], physical activities by location [300239664], physical activities by specific context [300239444], physical activities [300222722], Physical and Mental Activities (hierarchy name) [300222468], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
